{
  "stem": "490.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it's very little publicized, but that was the truth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Poles-- we heard the same things about the Russians as we did the Americans that knew the Russians after the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it's very, very uncomfortable even to talk about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Which today, they are-- everybody's considered friends, and we are trying to play up to these-- to countries which we don't want to know their past.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it is very unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I was left alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always alone, since I was-- I left my-- my parents died on me when I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I came to this-- to Ostrowca, because the school-- the-- At-- at the time, it was the [? dayan. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dayan, ?] it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The one who was in charge-- the principal of the school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew that I had no parents, and I would end up [BACKGROUND NOISE] doing like every Jew was doing there, doing their work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he thought that I deserved something better, because I was quite a-- a different, smart little boy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe they just liked me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he gave me a letter of recommendation, and I went to the big city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, from this day on, I was on my own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- in the beginning, you know, I ate every day in a different house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I slept with-- with strange places.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- many times I had to sleep at the-- at the school, because there was no room for me to sleep except on a bench.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to say who was with me, I would say that-- that God was with me, most of the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the way I felt, since I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow, I felt that-- that something was-- somebody was guiding you.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
